  "verse_id": "12.2",
  "mūla": {
    "devanāgarī": "मय्य् आवेश्य मनो ये मां नित्य-युक्ता उपासते | श्रद्धया परयोपेतास् ते मे युक्ततमा मताः",
    "iast": "mayy āveśya mano ye māṃ nitya-yuktā upāsate | śraddhayā parayopetās te me yuktatamā matāḥ",
    "chapter_position": "Chapter 12 (Bhakti-Yoga (The Yoga of Devotion)), verse 2",
    "speaker": "Krishna",
    "addressed_to": "Arjuna"
  },
